                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="developer">
                    <img src="~/images/dev4.jpeg" alt="Developer 6">
                    <h4>Timothy Doe</h4>
                    <p>Mobile UI/UX Designer</p>
                    <p class="dev-description">
                        Timothy is a skilled Flutter mobile developer who played a key role in driving the development of this mobile application.
